            . On the 22d of August I locked my door and went out about five o'clock; I returned home at seven in the evening. Then I missed the things mentioned in the indictment (repeating them). I never saw the prisoner till I saw her at Sir 
               <persName id="t17800913-5-person90">
                  John
                   Fielding
               <interp inst="t17800913-5-person90" type="surname" value="Fielding"></interp>
